        "Reminder: Your subscription is expiring soon.",
        "Your package has been shipped. Track its progress here.",
        "Win a luxury vacation! Enter now for a chance to win!",
        "Project update: We've made significant progress this week.",
        "Get rich quick! Invest in our revolutionary new system.",
        "Invoice #12345 is due on 2023-10-26.",
        "Limited-time offer: Buy one, get one free!",
        "Your order has been confirmed. Thank you for your purchase.",
        "Spam alert: Your email address has been selected for a special prize.",
